          ## install
          ```bash
            git clone -b gh-pages \
                https://github.com/bollwyvl/nb-mermaid.git \
                ~/.ipython/nbextensions/
          ```
          
          ## activate
          In the notebook...
          ```javascript
          %%javascript
          IPython.load_ipython_extensions(["nb-mermaid/nb-mermaid"]);
          ```

